{"id":492668166,"lang":"cpp","time":"1Â year","timestamp":1620919509,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"8 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/492668166/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Ambiguous Coordinates","memory":"9.3 MB","code":"class Solution {\npublic:\n    vector<string> ambiguousCoordinates(string S) {\n        vector<string> ans;\n        for (int i = 2; i < S.size() - 1; i++) {\n            string xStr = S.substr(1,i-1), yStr = S.substr(i, S.size() - 1 - i);\n            vector<string> xPoss;\n            for (int j = 0; j < xStr.size(); j++)\n                if (isValid(xStr, j))\n                    xPoss.push_back(xStr.substr(0,j) + (j ? \".\" : \"\") + xStr.substr(j));\n            for (int j = 0; j < yStr.size(); j++)\n                if (isValid(yStr, j)) {\n                    string y = yStr.substr(0,j) + (j ? \".\" : \"\") + yStr.substr(j);\n                    for (auto x : xPoss)\n                        ans.push_back(\"(\" + x + \", \" + y + \")\");\n                }\n        }\n        return ans;\n    }\n    \n    bool isValid(string str, int dec) {\n        if (dec && str[str.size()-1] == '0') return false;\n        if (str.size() != 1 && dec != 1 && str[0] == '0') return false;\n        return true;\n    }\n};","compare_result":"","title_slug":"ambiguous-coordinates"}
